    'home.reggiatrici.title': 'Strapping machines since 1947',
    'home.reggiatrici.text': 'We produce manual strapping machines and tensioners Made in Italy, synonymous with quality, resistance and reliability. Suitable for various industrial applications, each device has been designed to perform at its best under every effort. With Us, you will get not only superior quality strapping, but also the certainty of investing in packaging solutions designed to last over time and successfully face industrial challenges.',
