    'home.solutions.text': 'At F.lli Pozzi, you can choose from our range of manual strapping machines, and innovative and reliable solutions to meet the packaging needs of companies of every size and sector. Our experience in the sector allows us to fully understand the challenges of industrial packaging and provide personalized consultancy to guarantee the choice of products most suited to your needs.',
    'home.solutions.button': 'Packaging supplies',
