    // Azienda
    'azienda.paragraph1': 'Fratelli Pozzi was founded in 1947 in the Bergamo area as a small craft business: since then it has recorded continuous growth both in terms of product range and production capacity, transforming a small local activity into a real company developing a commercial network spread throughout much of the world.',
    'azienda.paragraph2': 'For over 70 years, the Company, a Leader in its sector, has distinguished itself for the high quality of its products, recognized worldwide for its "Made in Italy", and for the qualified assistance it is able to provide to its customers.',
    'azienda.paragraph3': 'The company has a modern warehouse with a surface area of 2200 sqm, inside which production, assembly of strapping machines, storage of all consumable materials and technical assistance for every type of strapping machine are carried out.',
