    // Descrizioni prodotti - Reggiatrici a batteria
    'prodotti.descriptions.GTSMART': 'Battery strapping machine for PP/PET strapping 13/16 mm vibration welding for flat and round packages. Adjustable tension up to 3000 N. For strapping thicknesses up to 1.0 mm. The 14V / 3.0 AH LI-ION battery recharges in just 15 minutes.',
    'prodotti.descriptions.GTONE': 'Battery strapping machine for PP/PET strapping 13/16/19 mm vibration welding for flat and round packages. Adjustable tension up to 3000 N. For strapping thicknesses from 0.8 to 1.2. The 14V / 3.0 AH LI-ION battery recharges in just 15 minutes.',
    'prodotti.descriptions.GTXTREME': 'Battery strapping machine for PET strapping 19/25 mm vibration welding for flat and round packages. Adjustable tension up to 5000 N. For strapping thicknesses up to 1.3 mm. The 14V / 3.0 AH LI-ION battery recharges in just 15 minutes.',
    'prodotti.descriptions.CP007': 'Battery strapping machine for PP/PET strapping 13/16 mm with manual tensioning and vibration welding, flat and round packages. Adjustable tension up to 2000 N. For strapping thicknesses up to 1.0 mm. The 14V / 3.0 AH LI-ION battery recharges in just 15 minutes.',
    'prodotti.descriptions.GTMAX': 'Battery strapping machine for PET strapping 19/25 mm vibration welding for flat and round packages. Adjustable tension up to 5000 N. For strapping thicknesses up to 1.3 mm. The 14V / 3.0 AH LI-ION battery recharges in just 15 minutes.',
    'prodotti.descriptions.VIPER': 'Battery strapping machine for PET strapping 9/12/16/19 mm vibration welding for flat and round packages. The tensioning force is programmable in Newtons, Kg and pounds. Featuring an innovative touchscreen interface. 18V / 3.0 AH LI-ION battery.',
    // Descrizioni prodotti - Reggiatrici pneumatiche vibrazione
    'prodotti.descriptions.FASTPNLT': 'Pneumatic strapping machine for PP/PET strapping 13/16/19 mm vibration welding for flat and round packages adjustable tension up to 2000 N – for strapping thicknesses up to 1 mm.',
    'prodotti.descriptions.FASTPNHIGHTENSION': 'Pneumatic strapping machine for Polyester strapping 19/25/32 mm vibration welding for flat and round packages adjustable tension up to 6000 N – for strapping thicknesses up to 1.3 mm.',
    // Descrizioni prodotti - Reggiatrici pneumatiche acciaio con sigillo
    'prodotti.descriptions.FP131619': 'Pneumatic strapping machine for steel strapping from 13, 16 and 19 mm, with F series seal (Overlap). Excellent for strapping round packages. Thickness from 0.5 to 0.6 mm. Weight: 4.5 kg.',
    'prodotti.descriptions.FP19S25S32S': 'Pneumatic strapping machine for steel strapping from 19, 25 and 32 mm, with F series seal (Overlap). Weighs only 10 kg and ideal for strapping flat and round packages, thickness from 0.8 to 0.9 mm.',
    'prodotti.descriptions.FP32PLUS': 'Pneumatic strapping machine for steel strapping from 19, 25 and 32 mm, with F series seal (Overlap). Thickness from 1.0 to 1.2 mm.',
    // Descrizioni prodotti - Reggiatrici pneumatiche acciaio senza sigillo
    'prodotti.descriptions.SL3PN': 'Pneumatic strapping machine without seal for steel strapping from 13, 16 and 19 mm. Max thickness 0.6 mm. Weight: 7 kg.',
    // Descrizioni prodotti - Carrelli
    'prodotti.descriptions.GM15': 'Strapping trolley for polypropylene coils 9-19 mm, complete with box to contain strapping machines and seals. Internal diameter from 390 or 405 mm.',
    'prodotti.descriptions.FP15': 'Strapping trolley for polypropylene coils 9-19 mm, complete with box to contain strapping machines and seals. Internal diameter from 150/200/280/405 mm.',
    'prodotti.descriptions.FP93': 'Strapping trolley for polyester and steel coils from 9-32 mm and internal diameter 405 and steel with wound 13-19 mm and internal diameter 405, complete with box to contain strapping machines and seals. Internal diameter from 390 or 405 mm.',
    'prodotti.descriptions.FP15S': 'Strapping trolley for polypropylene coils with internal diameter 200-280 mm. Complete with brake and box to contain strapping machines and seals.',
    'prodotti.descriptions.FP92': 'Strapping trolley for steel coils in single coil rolls from 13 to 32 mm, complete with box to contain strapping machines and seals.',
    'prodotti.descriptions.FP13': 'Strapping trolley for textile polyester coils with int. diam. 76 mm width 140 and 150 mm.',
    
